data.description: YOU HAVE TO SEE THIS HOME!!Recently updated home located on the south side of town, close to the shopping center, restaurants, and easy access to HWY 95.  Garage is boat deep with plenty of storage options, including a work bench. The peaceful backyard is beautifully landscaped and FULLY fenced.  Flat driveway and generous side parking for your RV or Boat. Large bedrooms, huge kitchen pantries and lots more storage in the big closets. Owned Solar and back up battery. Many upgrades including Designer interior paint, flooring and baseboards, R/O system, new garage door opener, keyless security lock and walk-in tub make this the perfect move-in ready home.
